   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**继续使用Product表，计算出按照登记日期（regist_date）升序进行排列的各日期的销售单价（sale_price）的总额。排序是需要将登记日期为\n",
    "NULL 的“运动 T 恤”记录排在第 1 位（也就是将其看作比其他日期都早）。**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "attachments": {
    "image.png": {
     "image/png": ""
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**代码**\n",
    "\n",
    "SELECT regist_date, product_name, sale_price,\n",
    "  SUM (sale_price) OVER (ORDER BY regist_date NULLS FIRST) AS current_sum_price\n",
    "  FROM Product;\n",
    "    \n",
    "    或者\n",
    "SELECT regist_date, product_name, sale_price,\n",
    "  SUM (sale_price) OVER (ORDER BY COALESCE(regist_date, CAST('0001-01-01' AS DATE))) AS current_sum_price\n",
    "  FROM Product;\n",
    "  \n",
    "**结果**\n",
    "![image.png](attachment:image.png)\n"
   ]
